# Hipcc standalone build artifacts produced by running
# `hipcc --genco` or bpf-bundling on the butterfly kernel from the
# magnum crate root. They're derivative and would bloat the repo.
/magnum_butterfly-hip-*

# Compiled kernel blobs in results/ (compiled at runtime by magnum-test,
# turbo-diag, bw-bench, dp4a-bench via hipcc --genco). Rebuildable.
/results/*.hsaco
